    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Jaeger UI 链接",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 34
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Trace 详情查看\n\n点击上方表格中的 **Trace ID** 列，或直接访问 **Jaeger UI**：\n\n```\nkubectl port-forward svc/jaeger-query -n sandbox-system 16686:16686\n```\n\n然后打开 http://localhost:16686\n\n在 Jaeger UI 中：\n- **Service** 选择 `sandbox-manager` 或 `sandbox-controller`\n- **Operation** 选择对应的操作（如 `POST /sandboxes`、`Reconcile` 等）\n- 点击 **Find Traces** 查看瀑布图"
      }
    }
  ]
}
